The '''National Center for Genome Resources (NCGR)''' is a nonprofit research organization in [[Santa Fe, New Mexico]] founded in 1994 focusing on [[life science]]s research, [[bioinformatics]] technologies, and leading-edge molecular data production including [[sequencing]] and [[Gene expression profiling|gene expression]].
